                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150215-79-defend674 t18150215-79-punish476"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs> aged 25.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex jury, before Mr. Justice Heath.</p>
